# Decrypted pallene build-server secrets, materialized by `make pallene-iso`
# immediately before the build and removed immediately after (see
# hosts/pallene/configuration.nix). The .placeholder files are NOT ignored —
# those are the committed dummy fallbacks `nix flake check` evaluates against.
secrets/pallene-secrets/binarylane-api-token
secrets/pallene-secrets/attic-push-token
